Package org.odpi.openmetadata.accessservices.analyticsmodeling.model.response

Class AnalyticsMessage

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.accessservices.analyticsmodeling.model.response.AnalyticsMessage
public class AnalyticsMessage extends Object
Generic error structure.
{
  "code": error code,
  "detail": explanation,
  "meta": {
   "severity": "error" || "info" || "warning"
  },
  "status": HTTP status code,
  "title": short description.
}
